data.description: This home is a beautiful ranch-style house with a full basement, where you can appreciate single-level living with a fully-finished lower level. There are many recent updates to the home that include a NEW roof, interior and exterior paint, an electric car charger, and re-finished hardwood floors. The basement features a bedroom, a den, a bathroom with a double vanity and jetted tub, and a large family room with a fireplace. The yard is completely fenced and includes fruit trees, gardening areas, and a great deck for entertaining. This home is a short distance from all the incredible trails on Powell Butte, and there are plenty of local areas for shopping, dining, and entertainment. [Home Energy Score = 5. HES Report at https://rpt.greenbuildingregistry.com/hes/OR10222257]
